  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was maybe smaller, but it was quite nice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my parents somehow managed to decorate it and to get still furniture, still the same old furniture, still the same old sofa that we-- that was from before the war, that we still managed to drag-- my mother somehow managed to save it until there, a big sofa with dark green covers.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was still there, and some other bits of furniture, not many, but they were still there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there were about two rooms in this flat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And somehow that flat was nice and I was keen on that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that was [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the whole area there, [POLISH] was on there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We always managed to put ourselves-- I think that was my parents didn't want to go into the most crowded part, so they always tried for the, in inverted commas, 'nice' part, nice area, which was not very easy.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But they still-- it was a really relatively pleasant place, where there were [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there were-- the people who lived there, they were mostly professionals or colleagues of my father.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And in this-- in those courtyards, by now in some of those courtyards, people were terribly deprived of green and of fresh air, because there was none.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there was this-- so people suddenly started digging up the courtyard and making little gardens in the courtyards with some vegetables.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't think there were many flowers, but there might have been some flowers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And there certainly were vegetables and they were growing vegetables in those courtyards.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I used to go into that garden and sit there and read, because I was absolutely crazy about reading, so I was always reading there, reading in this garden of the [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
